OL,6,FA mother has been jailed for causing
OL,7,Fthe death of her son in a crash on a
OL,8,Fblind bend in Dorset.
OL,10,F39 year old Barbara Roe from
OL,11,FLudgershall in Wiltshire, was driving
OL,12,Fwith her son on the A354 near East
OL,13,FWoodyates in North Dorset last March
OL,14,Fwhen she began travelling at speed.
OL,16,FShe then attempted to overtake a Ford
OL,17,FTransit as she approached a blind left-
OL,18,Fhand bend, crossing the solid white
OL,19,Fline marking in the middle of the road.
