OL,6,FA cattle transporter was travelling in
OL,7,Fthe opposite direction and Roe
OL,8,Fcollided with it.
OL,10,FMembers of the public attempted to
OL,11,Fgive first aid at the scene before the
OL,12,Femergency services attended.
OL,14,FHowever, despite their best efforts,
OL,15,FRoe's nine-year-old son Zac Roe died
OL,16,Fat the scene.
