OL,6,FPolice Constable Gavin Newbury, of the
OL,7,FSerious Collision Investigation Team
OL,8,F(SCIT), said: "This tragic case is the
OL,9,Fcruellest of reminders of the truly
OL,10,Fdevastating consequences that sadly
OL,11,Foccur when motorists drive in a
OL,12,Fdangerous or reckless manner.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts are absolutely with
OL,15,FZac's loved ones, who have been
OL,16,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,17,Fofficers throughout.
