OL,6,F"While we fully appreciate nothing
OL,7,Fwill ever make up for their loss, our
OL,8,Frole has been to diligently
OL,9,Finvestigate the circumstances of this
OL,10,Fcollision and bring the evidence
OL,11,Fbefore the courts to allow the justice
OL,12,Fprocess to follow its course."
OL,14,FRoe was sentenced to five years in
OL,15,Fprison and disqualified from driving
OL,16,Ffor a period of seven and a half years.
OL,18,FZac's father and his paternal
OL,19,Fgrandparents described him as a "much-
OL,20,Floved boy".
