OL,6,FIn a statement, they said: "His father
OL,7,Fadored him, as did we.
OL,9,F"He was a popular boy who had many
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,F"He had an amazing imagination. He
OL,13,Fjust loved making things out of Lego,
OL,14,Ftwigs, cardboard, string and Sellotape.
OL,16,F"Just the same as his dad did when he
OL,17,Fwas Zac's age.
OL,19,F"He was talented at drawing and spent
OL,20,Fmany hours adding detail to whatever
OL,21,Fhe drew.
