OL,6,F"We called him nature boy as he loved
OL,7,Fbeing outdoors, making dens, riding
OL,8,Fhis bike and scooter, playing parkour
OL,9,Fand army games.
OL,11,F"He just loved life. He was always
OL,12,Fsmiling.
OL,14,F"He should be here now enjoying his
OL,15,Flife.
