OL,6,F"Money has been raised and there in
OL,7,Fnow a therapy dog named after Zac.
OL,8,FThis is Zac's legacy as he loved dogs.
OL,9,FIf anyone one would like to donate in
OL,10,FZac's memory please go to the 'Dogs
OL,11,Ffor Health' Facebook page.
OL,13,F"We will never stop loving him.
OL,15,F"The good memories are too hard to
OL,16,Fthink about yet. But when we are ready
OL,17,Fto remember them, we will know how
OL,18,Fmuch he loved his short life, which
OL,19,Fwas brutally taken away.
